node.text:
Mayweather isn't just a boxer...he's a businessman. He's built a HUGE name for himself leading to an estimated $450M net worth(other networths have been reported for 2021).

His upfront fee for his fight against Paul was said to be $10M. Overall he reported he'll make between $50M and $100M.

This is the difference between him and many athletes...it takes a great businessman to be able to make big pay days like this.

Watch the ful video here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r4fcOyfVoLE&t=77s

Follow us @businessequity

Photo by Business Equity on August 13, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Ravi Abuvala @raviabuvala_ If you're a business owner, here are 6 practical ways you can bring in more money while doing less work. Let's get started'.

Photo by Business Equity on August 13, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'Ravi Abuvala @raviabuvala 1. Hire more people. know what you're thinking- "doesn't that make me ess money?" I'll explain why it doesn't end up making you less later in the thread.'.

Photo by Business Equity on August 13, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'Ravi Abuvala @raviabuvala 2. Outline everything. You need guides for every task in M Map out what to do, how to do it, and any resource that may be needed.'.

Photo by Business Equity on August 13, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Ravi Abuvala @raviabuvala_ 3. Take some time off. Believe it or not, taking time off will help you relax and put more intentional effort into your business. You don't need to grind 24/7.'.

Photo by Business Equity on August 13, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'RaviAbua Ravi Abuvala @raviabuvala_ aau 4. Stop doing ousy work You don't make more money just because you're "hUsTliNg" 4 hours of concentrated work is more productive than 12 12 hours of distracted work.'.

Photo by Business Equity on August 13, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Ravi Abuvala @raviabuvala_ 5. Train virtual assistants. Once you have outlines for everything, it becomes much easier to hire VAs to fulfill your day-to-day tasks. They're going to help free up your time from the day-to-day tasks.'.

Photo by Business Equity on August 13, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'Ravi Abuvala @raviabuvala 6. Create systems. "You should be working or your business, not in your business." Systems allow you to have your employees run your business for you while you focus on bringing in more revenue.'.

Photo by Business Equity on August 13, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Ravi Abuvala @raviabuvala_ Hiring more people to do the day- day-to- day work may seem like an expense in the short term. But long term, you get your time back from doing those tasks and you can focus on what makes the most money. If your time is worth $350 hour, you shouldn't do $10/hour hour tasks.'.

Photo by Business Equity on August 13, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Ravi Abuvala @raviabuvala_ help business owners scale their businesses through implementing systems. This isn't for beginners, only business owners who want their time back while making more money. If this is something you're interested in, follow me.'.

The idea is to invest in things that are actually changing peoples lives...those things are much more likely to stay around longer and actually make money.

For example, investing into Amazon 2 decades ago could have brought a HUGE return on investment, and its a company that actually makes peoples lives easier.

Follow us @businessequity

node.text:
Breaking generational cycles isn't for the weak.

This is what we mean when we say don't listen to your friends, family and neighbors. We're not saying to never speak to them again, but you have a goal and if you're serious about reaching that goal you're going to have to block out the noise

Follow us @businessequity

node.text:
We all have the same amount of time in our days.

If you work a 9-5 it's likely that you have 2 days off a week. If you hate your current job don't slack off on the weekend. You have 48 hours (at the minimum for the entire week) to make a change.

The opportunites are endless...you can start a side hustle from basically anything. 

Follow us @businessequity
